Class Book

java.lang.Object
Book
public class Book
extends java.lang.Object
The book class is responsible for creating the book object with the variables that consist of its serial number, name, published date, and if it is checked out. We also override the string so so that the previously mentioned components are formatted a certain way when printed.
Author:
Nida Ansari, Cecelia Chollette-Dickson
